title: #92Noon Montage/Snob/Moss/KG&BA/Florio
description: Wild lost last night, so we lament. Then Stump the Snob to finish the first hour. Mitch Moss from VSIN offers the Vegas perspective on the Wild series, Gorg and Arrigoni have pucks and ponies, then Florio closes the show!
